criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  both sex;

          -  65 years and older;

          -  hospital stay less than 48 hours;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  cancer in the last 5 years;

          -  delirium;

          -  cognitive deficit that impossibility the patient to read and sign the informed consent
             form;

          -  neurological disease;

          -  neurodegenerative muscular disease;

          -  impossibility to receive the intervention.
